title: How I feel
content: I am a little anxious. But I know I need to calm down.

title: What I want to do next?
content: I want to become the best sports person possible.

title: How I should feel?
content: I should be happy because I got an internship.

title: A Perfect Morning
content: "I woke up early today and went for a walk. The sky was a beautiful shade of orange and the breeze was gentle. I felt so refreshed and motivated. I even got to finish reading that book I love. Just a really peaceful, happy start to the day."

title: Missing the Old Days
content: Lately, I’ve been thinking a lot about how things used to be. I miss spending time with my childhood friends, and it feels like life is moving too fast. I feel a bit lost and nostalgic, and sometimes I just want to pause everything and rest.

title: Tired of Being Ignored
content: It’s so frustrating when people don’t listen to me. I keep trying to be patient and understanding, but I’m always the one who ends up being taken for granted. I need to start setting boundaries because this is not okay anymore.
